  "title": "Sales Executive (Showroom / Outdoor) #81690",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building Completion and Finishing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive (Showroom / Outdoor)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (9:00 AM – 5:00 PM) (off on weekdays)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Bonus + Commission</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Promote vanity counters and accessories to customers and industry contacts.</li><li>Prepare quotations and follow up on enquiries.</li><li>Support marketing campaigns and product presentations.</li><li>Maintain good customer service standards.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the department head</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Able to communicate clearly and work well with customers.</li><li>Sales experience or knowledge of the interior design and renovation industry is an advantage.</li><li>Self-motivated and goal oriented.</li><li>Having your own transport is advantage for outdoor role</li><li>Candidates with no relevant experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81690 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
